rows.label: tev025701_MSG0001
rows.name:
Dude, will someone PLEASE grow a freaking brain and
put some walls around this maintenance area?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0002
rows.name:
If a tyrant decides to fly in here while all our Skells are
deadlined, we're as good as screwed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0003
rows.name:
When I complained, the higher-ups told me I should
just learn to take down tyrants with ground gear.
I do not have enough middle fingers to respond to that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0004
rows.name:
Sure, with the right equipment and augments, we can
do some amazing stuff on the ground. But that doesn't
mean we should hang our Skells out to dry![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0010
rows.name:
Have you met that chick in the Outfitters test hangar
who can't stop talking about Skells?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0013
rows.name:
The Outfitters are crazy to let her anywhere near their
latest weapons. She's barely seen combat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0014
rows.name:
They should leave the tests to a battle-tested team like
mine instead of that...Skellophile weirdo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0015
rows.name:
Oh, just you wait. They're inviting disaster.
Let's hope nobody gets hurt...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0024
rows.name: Where the hell did those alien kitty cats come from?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0025
rows.name:
Team Belisarda had to take off and provide combat 
support out in the streets. Left us all alone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0026
rows.name:
And what were we supposed to do? I'm a gun person,
you know? I can't keep up with that kind of close-
range ninjitsu crap.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0027
rows.name:
And now the bastards got the Skell in the restricted
hangar and hurt a whole bunch of the crew.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0043
rows.name:
What was all that business that just went down in front
of the hangar?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0044
rows.name:
I saw Commander Vandham come running by with a
whole bunch of angry-looking BLADEs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0045
rows.name:
But did anyone say anything to me? Nooooo!
Why do they always leave Outfitters out of the loop?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0050
rows.name:
Team Belisarda's leader is a class freaking act,
let me tell you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0051
rows.name:
Not only does he steal the black Skell,
but he decides to smash our door in the process![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0052
rows.name:
I really feel bad for his dead teammates.
Their sacrifice was for THIS guy? Seriously?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0057
rows.name:
Now that we've tracked down the Lifehold Core,
I say it's time to let things slide.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0058
rows.name: I think Lao's been punished enough already.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0059
rows.name:
And his teammates will be brought back to life in the
end anyway, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG0060
rows.name:
Really, there's no point in worrying about the past.
What's done is done, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG1001
rows.name:
You'll be interested to know I laid it all out on Camber.
Told him everything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG1002
rows.name:
Of course, I remembered to mention Alexa's unhealthy
infatuation with tall, dark, and handsome Skells.
Leave no detail out, says me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG1003
rows.name:
But guess what? He didn't seem to care at ALL!
All he did was laugh and mutter something about how
he isn't sure which one of us is crazier.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG1004
rows.name:
I guess I owe her one. Without Alexa, I might never
have learned how to talk to Camber like we're actually
on the same level.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG2001
rows.name:
The Ganglion showed up not long after the test went
south.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG2002
rows.name:
The two of us weren't able to put up much of a fight.
Bastards had us up against a wall.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG2003
rows.name:
We tried to jettison our Skells and run, but they picked
off Hannah before I even knew what was happening.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG2004
rows.name:
I just kept running until my legs went numb,
and that's when Alexa showed up and saved me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025701_MSG2005
rows.name:
I honestly never thought I'd see Camber again.
But now that I've got him back, I'm gonna stay here
and keep it that way![ST:wait ]
